# Detailed Repository Structure

```
virtual-hospitals-africa/
├── deno.json            # Project tasks & dependencies
├── chatbot              # Chatbot processes to respond to messages via WhatsApp Cloud API
│   ├── patient          # Patient chatbot
│   ├── pharmacist       # Pharmacist chatbot
├── components           # Preact components not requiring client-side javascript (hooks)
│   ├── library          # Design system
├── db                   # Postgres Database
│   ├── dumps            # Database Dumps
│   ├── migrations       # Chronological database migrations
│   ├── models           # Database functions
│   ├── resources        # Raw files used by seeds
│   ├── scripts          # TS & Shell scripts
│   └── seed             # Loading seed data
├── db.d.ts              # Auto-generated types of our database; regenerate via deno task db:codegen
├── docker-compose.yml   # Docker Compose configurations
├── Dockerfile*          # Container definitions
├── events               # Asynchonous events processing
├── external-clients     # External dependencies
├── islands              # Preact components requiring client-side javascript (hooks)
├── routes               # Web-accessible routes
│   ├── app              # The primary web application for health workers
│   ├── chatbot          # WhatsApp Cloud API webhook
│   ├── regulator        # The regulator web application
├── scripts              # Grab bag of useful TS & shell scripts
├── shared               # Logic that can be safely shared (imported) by client & server
├── static               # Static files served by web server
├── tailwind.config.ts   # Core styles
├── test                 # Tests
│   ├── chatbot          # Chatbot tests
│   ├── events           # Event tests
│   ├── islands          # Island tests
│   ├── models           # Model tests
│   ├── shared           # Shared tests
│   ├── util             # Utility tests
│   └── web              # Round trip web tests
├── types.ts             # Dictionary of composite types not part of db.d.ts; Put new types here instead
└── util                 # Utility functions
├── .github/             # GitHub workflows

```
